item.title: 2025 Azerbaijan Driver Ratings | Grid Talk Formula 1 Podcast
item.description:
Tom and Jawad are back with another driver ratings show, giving you their rundown of each driver out of 10. Join them both as they grade the two title protagonists weekends, a surprise podium and a Super Max masterclass around the streets of Baku.

Did anyone score a perfect 10, or did anyone only get points for turning up last weekend? Be sure to listen to find out!
